🧠 Corpus Callosum Layer (CCL) v1.0 — Formal Spec

0. One-Line Definition

CCL = a high-bandwidth semantic bus that enables translation, synchronization, and compositional execution across heterogeneous AI subsystems while preserving provenance, confidence, and constraints.

⸻

1. Position in the Stack

           ┌───────────────────────────────┐
           │        Pantheon Nucleus       │
           │ (Router / Combinator / Memory)│
           └──────────────┬────────────────┘
                          │
                ┌─────────▼─────────┐
                │  Corpus Callosum  │
                │       Layer       │
                │   (Semantic Bus)  │
                └─────────┬─────────┘
                          │
     ┌───────────┬────────┼────────┬───────────┐
