This is the heart of the CCL.

{
  "id": "uuid",
  "type": "observation | inference | plan | action | artifact",
  "content": {},
  "embedding": null,
  "source": {
    "module": "VLM",
    "model": "vision_v1",
    "timestamp": "ISO8601"
  },
  "confidence": 0.82,
  "provenance": [
    {"step": "image_caption", "module": "VLM"},
    {"step": "interpretation", "module": "LLM"}
  ],
  "relations": {
    "depends_on": [],
    "contradicts": [],
    "supports": []
  },
  "constraints": {
    "verified": false,
    "requires_review": false
  }
}

👉 Everything becomes one of these objects.

This is your interlingua.

