4. Internal Subsystems of CCL

4.1 Translation Engine
	•	input: raw model output
	•	output: canonical object

Adapters per model:
	•	LLMAdapter
	•	VLMAdapter
	•	AgentAdapter
	•	RetrievalAdapter

⸻

4.2 Message Bus

Implements:

publish(object)
subscribe(module, filter)
route(object, target_modules)

Supports:
	•	broadcast
	•	targeted routing
	•	priority queues

⸻

4.3 State Manager

Maintains:
	•	session state
	•	working memory
	•	global context

Operations:

update_state(object)
query_state(filters)
snapshot()
rollback()


⸻

4.4 Conflict Resolver

Detects:
	•	contradictions
	•	low-confidence collisions
	•	incompatible plans

Logic:

if contradiction:
    send_to(Hound)
    send_to(Mirror)
    annotate(object)


⸻

4.5 Provenance Tracker

Immutable log:

append(object)
trace(object_id)
verify_chain(object_id)

This is your Checksum spine in practice.

⸻

4.6 Synchronization Engine

Ensures:
	•	all modules see same state slice
	•	no stale data

Techniques:
	•	versioned state
	•	timestamp ordering
	•	causal linking

